ning","sortindex":"1","primaryname":"1","translit":"Prowl: Clans & Cunning"},"alternatenames":[],"description":"<p><em><strong>Prowl</strong></em> is a quick, competitive, highly interactive strategy card game for 2 to 5 players.</p>\n\n<p>By manipulating the various animal factions, players scheme to ensure that the one they&rsquo;ve secretly chosen emerges on top.</p>\n\n<p>Do you favour the brute strength of Autumn, or Spring&rsquo;s insidious magic? What of Winter&rsquo;s corrupt officials, or Summer&rsquo;s desperate sellswords? Every clan has a host of colourful characters, each with their own special abilities.</p>\n\n<p>Pit the clans against each other, switch sides to keep your enemies guessing, and accuse your opponents to forestall their plans.</p>\n\n<p>As conflict threatens the animal kingdom, your only loyalty lies with the victor.</p>\n\n<p><em>&mdash;description from the publisher</em></p>\n\n","wiki":"<span class='text-muted'>This page does not exist. You can edit this page to create it.</span>","website":{"url":false},"imageid":"8425185","images":{"thumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/fSLgcssoLlPwjzHYPtI5xA__small/img/8jIRtwjNCbajydKoPNCDjl48ULM=/fit-in/200x150/filters:strip_icc()/pic8425185.png","micro":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/fSLgcssoLlPwjzHYPtI5xA__micro/img/MKn_lOvKnAjaDenDMnQV8eukUWw=/fit-in/64x64/filters:strip_icc()/pic8425185.png","square":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/fSLgcssoLlPwjzHYPtI5xA__square/img/jObd0gf9MUf7Baib8OoqxjZsafQ=/75x75/filters:strip_icc()/pic8425185.png","tallthumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/fSLgcssoLlPwjzHYPtI5xA__tallthumb/img/N1W1LGr9KsdIch0MJqjBOqplpQM=/fit-in/75x125/filters:strip_icc()/pic8425185.png","previewthumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/fSLgcssoLlPwjzHYPtI5xA__previewthumb/img/1R8zd05UV-fP7uBJ4QQgwpMjXYE=/fit-in/300x320/filters:strip_icc()/pic8425185.png","square200":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/fSLgcssoLlPwjzHYPtI5xA__square200/img/BHHfqRVayL7YnoDa4iMZ--a7cds=/200x200/filters:strip_icc()/pic842518